      "name": "Nurture Exit — Reply Detected",
      "description": "Separate GHL workflow. Trigger: Customer Replied while in nurture. Removes contact from the nurture workflow, creates an immediate follow-up task, tags 'nurture-converted-to-active'."
    },
    {
      "name": "Nurture Exit — Booking Detected",
      "description": "Separate GHL workflow. Trigger: Appointment Booked while in nurture. Removes contact from nurture workflow, tags 'nurture-converted-booked'."
